name: So Blessed The Model "Limited Edition" Poster #1
description:
So Blessed the Model's debut poster drops November 29th. Be the first to purchase her "Limited Edition" poster by placing your pre-order TODAY!! All pre-orders will receive a singed poster and a surprise gift from So Blessed. Hurry and pre-order your poster TODAY this "Special" offer ends November 25th.

*CLEVELAND ONLY* Your poster can be delivered or picked up at So Blessed The Models meet n greet on November 29th. Please specify this when you make your purchase.
